GUY WHO ORDERS STRIKE 
ON PEARL HARBOR.

88
00:03:16,821 --> 00:03:18,656
- I DON'T KNOW WHY 
YOU'RE NOT TAKING THIS

89
00:03:18,656 --> 00:03:20,325
"I'M OUT OF HERE" SERIOUSLY,

90
00:03:20,325 --> 00:03:23,661
BUT I AM OUT OF HERE, 
SERIOUSLY.

91
