- TELL ME. WHEN?

93
00:03:29,542 --> 00:03:31,711
- THAT'S IT. 
I'M OUT OF HERE.

94
00:03:35,756 --> 00:03:36,882
TA-DA!

95
00:03:36,882 --> 00:03:38,551
I'M OUT OF HERE.

96
00:03:38,551 --> 00:03:40,261
- [man on radio] 
WE GOT THE ATTACKING

97
00:03:40,261 --> 00:03:41,804
ANIMAL DOWN.

98
00:03:41,804 --> 00:03:44,181
- I'M OUT OF THIS FAMILY, 
SERIOUSLY.

99
00:03:44,181 --> 00:03:46,267
THIS TIME WE'RE GONNA BE 
SO FAR AWAY, YOU'LL NEVER

100
00:03:46,267 --> 00:03:48,185
BE ABLE TO FIND US.

101
00:03:48,185 --> 00:03:50,145
- WE'RE GOIN' TO PHOENIX. 
- DON'T TELL 'EM WHERE.

102
00:03:50,145 --> 00:03:52,147
- I-I JUST THOUGHT-- 
- IT DOESN'T MATTER WHY.

103
00:03:52,147 --> 00:03:54,692
- MICHAEL, MAYBE THE REASON 
WHY YOU ALWAYS COME BACK...

104
00:03:54,692 --> 00:03:56,652
IS BECAUSE YOU NEED US 
MORE THAN WE NEED YOU.

105
00:03:56,652 --> 00:03:58,863
- [scoffs] 
OH, THAT'S RICH.

106
00:03:58,863 --> 00:04:02,992
HUH. I NEED YOU. 
ALL RIGHT, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

107
00:04:02,992 --> 00:04:05,828
MOM, YOU'RE ALWAYS ASKING ME 
TO HELP YOU LOOK AFTER BUSTER.

108
00:04:05,828 --> 00:04:08,498
YOU CAN FIND SOMEBODY ELSE. 
I HOPE SHE DOESN'T KILL YOU.

109
