YOU'RE TONED AND FIT.

216
00:08:00,646 --> 00:08:02,690
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING? 
- I'M EXERCISING, MICHAEL.

217
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:04,859
I SEE YOU FOUND AN EXERCISE 
TAPE MADE FOR PEOPLE

218
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:06,569
AS LAZY AS YOU ARE.

219
00:08:06,569 --> 00:08:09,279
- I DO HAVE A LOVE LIFE. 
- TIGHTEN, ONE, TWO, THREE.

220
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:11,323
- OKAY, THIS IS GOING OFF.

221
00:08:11,323 --> 00:08:13,033
ONE NIGHT IN THE MASTER BEDROOM,

222
00:08:13,033 --> 00:08:15,495
AND YOU GOT YOURSELF 
A LOVE LIFE AGAIN?

223
00:08:15,495 --> 00:08:17,788
- WELL, I'LL BE HONEST. 
